This paper discusses the visibility of scientific publications in Latin America and the Caribbean, which falls under the categories of digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), social networks (cs.SI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper specifically focuses on the Web of Science and the SciELO Citation Index, which are both relevant to these sub-categories.
